{"tid":1103390,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"GTX 10 系顯示卡正式支援光線追蹤技術！","createTime":"2019-04-12T11:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T15:00:05.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"73efdb025b2af1cde58c0f02a44ac62aed619762","tid":1103390,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/nvidia/61418/nvidia推出新款geforce-game-ready-425-31-whql驅動，在光線追蹤上gtx-1660-ti與gtx-1080一樣/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fnvidia%2F61418%2Fnvidia%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E6%96%B0%E6%AC%BEgeforce-game-ready-425-31-whql%E9%A9%85%E5%8B%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%89%E7%B7%9A%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4%E4%B8%8Agtx-1660-ti%E8%88%87gtx-1080%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A3%2F&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8PS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=a8dc0995\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/nvidia/61418/nvidia推出新款geforce-game-ready-425-31-whql驅動，在光線追蹤上gtx-1660-ti與gtx-1080一樣/</a><br />\n<br />\nNVIDIA終於發布了最新的GeForce Game Ready WHQL驅動，該驅動支援在GeForce GTX GPU上支援Microsoft的DXR API。NVIDIA上個月在GDC 2019上宣布了最新的驅動，允許非RTX顯示卡為用戶提供渲染即時光線追蹤效果的能力。隨著現在的驅動的推出GeForce GTX GPU的擁有者可以嘗試一些頂級AAA遊戲中的即時光線追蹤功能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-20-Series-Turing-Graphics-Cards-Gaming.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-20-Series-Turing-Graphics-Cards-Gaming.jpg&h=25cec558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNVIDIA推出最新的GeForce Game Ready WHQL驅動 &ndash; 為GeForce GTX GPU啟用光線追蹤，在GeForce Game Ready 425.31 WHQL驅動中能夠支援為微軟DXR即時光線追蹤的功能。為了實現這一點，你需要以下這些顯示卡，NVIDIA GeForce Game Ready WHQL支援一系列GeForce GTX和舊版Titan卡，其中包括：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019-03-18_23-28-23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F2019-03-18_23-28-23.png&h=7fefa09e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNVIDIA GeForce RTX卡經過設計，擁有架構增強功能，可執行RTX功能，如光線追蹤陰影，反射，全區照明和環境光遮擋。GeForce RTX系列採用專用的Tensor和RT核心設計與GeForce GTX系列的傳統渲染方法相比，它們可以使光線追蹤速度提高2-3倍。現在有了這個驅動，GeForce GTX顯示卡將能夠在傳統著色器核心上執行光線追蹤指令，但不會像RTX那樣快。據NVIDIA稱有做光線追踪的幾種技術，每種技術的性能影響取決於幾個方面。但到目前為止發布的所有AAA級遊戲（Shadow of The Tomb Raider, Battlefield V, Metro Exodus）都依賴於單一技術。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-Update-GeForce-GTX-RTX-Driver_1-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-Update-GeForce-GTX-RTX-Driver_1-1.png&h=c2a4e18c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c633dfa2cc56f55aec1958b01ae5a1e3fc9465fb","tid":1103390,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:20:23.000Z","msg":"正如您在性能圖表中所看到的(更多圖表在消息來源)，GeForce RTX卡在許多場景中提供了相當大的RTX加速。這完全歸功於他們的RTX特定GPU架構增強功能。同時您還可以看到GeForce GTX 1660 Ti幾乎與GTX 1080一樣快，儘管計算能力較低。NVIDIA表示採用Turing GPU架構的GeForce 16系列顯示卡可以利用浮點和整數核心進行光線追蹤渲染，因為它與整數數學有很大關係，即使它們沒有RT核心或Tensor核心，由於GPU的升級，它們仍然可以提供更好的性能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-Update-GeForce-GTX-RTX-Driver_2-1-1480x833-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-Update-GeForce-GTX-RTX-Driver_2-1-1480x833-1.png&h=656b2367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-Update-GeForce-GTX-RTX-Driver_8-1480x833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-Update-GeForce-GTX-RTX-Driver_8-1480x833.png&h=abdbf5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-Update-GeForce-GTX-RTX-Driver_3-1-1480x833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-Update-GeForce-GTX-RTX-Driver_3-1-1480x833.png&h=3a247531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wccftech.com/nvidia-geforce-game-ready-driver-geforce-gtx-ray-tracing-rtx-features-enabled/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwccftech.com%2Fnvidia-geforce-game-ready-driver-geforce-gtx-ray-tracing-rtx-features-enabled%2F&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8PS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=5b3dbbaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://wccftech.com/nvidia-geforce-game-ready-driver-geforce-gtx-ray-tracing-rtx-features-enabled/</a>"},{"pid":"92da35c34c801f18c8a6090c0b1032c42a7fa4a7","tid":1103390,"uid":84415,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:21:02.000Z","msg":"連同負優化patch一同 releases <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6e88bd3b4ef61a4bd575e70adbde70dddef9c6","tid":1103390,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:24:26.000Z","msg":"用完之後Lag機到爆炸"},{"pid":"2398412eb669fdb2efdd2bd83428b03d6da61f88","tid":1103390,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:33:06.000Z","msg":"用完有冇10fps"},{"pid":"af2426e755659a869cfb24dd961f38825d48c447","tid":1103390,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2398412eb669fdb2efdd2bd83428b03d6da61f88","tid":1103390,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:33:06.000Z","msg":"用完有冇10fps"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wccftech.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/battlefield-v-medium-dxr-1920x1080-geforce-gpu-performance.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t